OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773821068
OL,3,C'The defining technology of our era':
OL,4,CChancellor bets on AI to boost UK
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,FThe UK will embrace AI faster than any
OL,8,Fother G7 nation in a bid to boost
OL,9,Fgrowth and investment, the chancellor
OL,10,Fis set to promise in a major economic
OL,11,Fspeech.
OL,13,FRachel Reeves will make her case at
OL,14,Fthe annual Mais lecture - an event for
OL,15,Fbank bosses, chancellors and prime
OL,16,Fministers to set out their economic
OL,17,Fvision - on Tuesday afternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773821068
OL,3,C'The defining technology of our era':
OL,4,CChancellor bets on AI to boost UK
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,FFollowing the launch of a landmark
OL,8,F#2.5 billion AI funding package,
OL,9,FReeves will argue that putting the UK
OL,10,Fat the forefront of the AI revolution
OL,11,Fwill drive growth and investment - and
OL,12,Fensure that "the technologies of the
OL,13,Ffuture" are "invented, built and
OL,14,Fdeployed here in Britain".
OL,16,FReeves will warn against "burying our
OL,17,Fheads in the sand" on AI, calling the
OL,18,Ftechnology "the defining technology of
OL,19,Four era".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773821068
OL,3,C'The defining technology of our era':
OL,4,CChancellor bets on AI to boost UK
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,F"We can leave it to the market alone,
OL,8,Fand let the balance of risk and reward
OL,9,Fbe determined by a super-wealthy few.
OL,10,FOr we can chart our own course," she
OL,11,Fwill say.
OL,13,FAnd despite fears that AI could wipe
OL,14,Fout millions of jobs, the chancellor
OL,15,Fwill promise that her strategy will
OL,16,Fboost employment, creating more than
OL,17,F100k jobs and #212 billion of
OL,18,Finvestment over the next two decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773821068
OL,3,C'The defining technology of our era':
OL,4,CChancellor bets on AI to boost UK
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,FShe says these will come largely from
OL,8,Fher ambition to "lead the quantum
OL,9,Frevolution", as the UK will become the
OL,10,Ffirst country in the world to commit
OL,11,Fto rolling out quantum computers at
OL,12,Fscale.
OL,14,FQuantum is a new type of computer
OL,15,Ftechnology that uses physics to
OL,16,Fprocess more data and solve more
OL,17,Fcomplex problems than traditional
OL,18,Fcomputers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773821068
OL,3,C'The defining technology of our era':
OL,4,CChancellor bets on AI to boost UK
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,FITV News has previously reported on
OL,8,Fhow quantum technology is helping to
OL,9,Fmake improvements in healthcare,
OL,10,Fincluding in identifying the early
OL,11,Fsigns of life-limiting conditions.
OL,13,FNearly all of the new AI money the
OL,14,Fgovernment has announced will go
OL,15,Ftowards investment in this area, with
OL,16,Ffunding targeted at buying new quantum
OL,17,Fcomputers, training experts and
OL,18,Fbacking research and existing
OL,19,Fcompanies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773821068
OL,3,C'The defining technology of our era':
OL,4,CChancellor bets on AI to boost UK
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,F#500 million will also go towards
OL,8,FBritish AI companies - money which the
OL,9,Fgovernment will launch in full this
OL,10,FApril.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FA focus on quantum and AI is one part
OL,18,Fof what Reeves will call the "three
OL,19,Fbiggest opportunities for economic
OL,20,Fgrowth in the UK".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
