PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773821068
OL,3,C'The defining technology of our era':
OL,4,CChancellor bets on AI to boost UK
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,FThe Chancellor will also outline how
OL,8,Fcloser ties with Europe and
OL,9,Fprioritising regional prosperity are
OL,10,Falso central to her economic
OL,11,Fphilosophy - with her policies set to
OL,12,Ffocus on how the UK can align more
OL,13,Fclosely with EU regulation to make
OL,14,Ftrade with the bloc easier.
OL,16,FReeves is hoping her priorities will
OL,17,Fimprove the UK's economic prospects,
OL,18,Famidst rising oil prices and global
OL,19,Feconomic uncertainty as a result of
OL,20,Fthe war in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
